Class SurveyObjects

  • java.lang.Object
    • SurveyObjects

  • public class SurveyObjects
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to define objects relevant to the data from the survey results. Each attribute of an object of type 'SurveyObjects' is a heading in the table of data that was read in. Each object created will be stored in ArrayList for later use.
    Author:
    armondluthens
